== Part 2: Dragon Quest II ==

=== Premise ===

A century later, Hargon the evil priest destroys Moonbrooke. Three descendants of Erdrick must unite to stop him.

=== Getting Started ===

==== Midenhall Castle ====

Starting location:
# Receive quest from King
# Depart solo
# Find your cousins

==== Finding Companions ====

===== Prince of Cannock =====

First companion:
* Chase him through towns
* Eventually recruit him
* Hybrid fighter/mage

===== Princess of Moonbrooke =====

Second companion:
* Cursed into dog form
* Need Ra's Mirror
* Full mage class

=== The Quest ===

==== Ship ====

Essential for exploration:
* Enables sea travel
* Opens world map
* Quest to obtain

==== Collecting Crests ====

